ri vilbert  jean gabin  curd jürgenskenneth more  bourvil  anthony franciosa  alec guinness  james stewart  john mills  toshiro mifune  burt lancaster  albert finney  tom courtenay  toshiro mifune  jacques perrin  ljubiša samardžić  john marley  – guy boydgeorge dzundzadavid alan griermitchell lichtensteinmatthew modinemichael wright  naseeruddin shah  gérard depardieu  carlo delle piane  hugh grantjames wilby  don amechejoe mantegna  marcello mastroiannimassimo troisi  oleg borisov  river phoenix  jack lemmon  fabrizio bentivogliomarcello mastroianni  xia yuroberto citran  götz georgeian hart  liam neesonchris penn  wesley snipes  sean penn  jim broadbent  javier bardem  –present luigi lo cascio  stefano accorsi  sean penn  javier bardem  david strathairn  ben affleck  brad pitt  silvio orlando  colin firth  vincent gallo  michael fassbender  philip seymour hoffmanjoaquin phoenix  themis panou  adam driver  fabrice luchini  oscar martínez  authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     gnd  sudoc  bnf cbg data musicbrainz bcefdaeab bne xx retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlejamesstewartoldid categories indiana county pennsylvania births deathsthcentury american male actorsthcentury american poetsthcentury presbyteriansacademy honorary award recipientsamerican male film actorsamerican male poetsamerican male radio actorsamerican male stage actorsamerican male television actorsamerican male voice actorsamerican male writersamerican military personnel of the vietnam waramerican military personnel of world war iiamerican people of scottish descentamerican presbyteriansbest actor academy award winnersbest drama actor golden globe television winnersbroadway theatre peopleburials at forest lawn memorial park glendalecalifornia republicanscecil b demille award golden globe winnersdeaths from pulmonary embolismdiseaserelated deaths in californiakennedy center honoreesmale actors from beverly hills californiamale actors from pennsylvaniamale western 