ressing critical issues like national security energy independence economic development and an improved environment soon thereafter i put behind me a successful career in the entertainment industry to assist in bringing to reality the first commercial united statesbased facility to produce biofuels and electricity from organic wastesfor these efforts and my other contributions to the industry i have three times been recognized as one of the “top  people in the bioeconomy” in worldwide polls of the readers of biofuels digestcareer highlightssustainable earth partners llc currently a cofounding principal offering services in renewable energy consulting technology commercialization and ecoindustrial project development stern brothers  cofour years as a strategic consultant to the alternative energy practice of this industryleading investment bank focusing on biobased technology project finance via the institutional bond marketsnew planet energy llcbioengineering resources incsevenyear association with the development and commercialization of a technology for the conversion of organic wastes to biofuels and renewable electricity first with bri then with new planet energy cofounded new planet energy llc and served for three years as its vice president – marketing  public affairsthe walt disney companythirteen years in marketing corporate governmental and investor relations at the walt disney companyattaining the title of vice presidentcorporate relations and assistant to the president overseeing the public affairs of one of the world’s bestknown high visibility corporate entities while also serving for eleven years as assistant to the company’s presidentchief operating officerexperiencevice president business developmenttechnikon llcjuly  – present  years  montheducationuniversity of southern californiaba cinematelevision mba financeba cinematelevision mba financeskillsmicrosoft excelmicrosoft wordpowerpointteachingpublic speakingrenewable energyhows this translationgreat•has errorsthanks for your helphonors  awardsprimary community involvement• president american friends of the edinburgh festival • member academy of motion picture arts and sciences• member board of directors of the los angeles chamber orchestra for twenty years serving on its executive finance endowment marketing and artistic liaison committees • founder and first chairman of the los angeles philharmonic business  professional committee which raises funds for the orchestra in the corporate community view james’ full profile tosee who you know in commonget introducedcontact james directlyview james’ full profileview this profile in another languageenglishgermanpeople also viewedclark stilwellpresident at land investment services llcthomas poitierchief financial officer at interdenominational theological centerdr al sutton md mhastudent at wusomlawrence r garrison srceo and president of lrg associates llc hbculeea executive board member campus police officer  tupdfrancisco boshellrenewable energy markets and standards analystjarrett carter srpublisher hbcu digestrandy ragondirector of development at edc technologyroderick andrewsassociate director of financial aid at university of north floridadaniel whitedirector of business operations at kentucky christian universityivonne molinacustomer services representativepublic profile badgeinclude this linkedin profile on other websitesview profile badgessearch by nameover  million professionals are already on linkedin find who you knowfirst namelast nameexample jeff weinerlinkedin member directoryabcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzmorebrowse members by country james b stewart  wikipedia james b stewart from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search james b stewart born james bennett stewart c  age – quincy illinois occupation nonfiction writer lawyer journalist nationality american period –present notable works den of thieves notable awards pulitzer prize for explanatory journalism  website jamesbstewartnet james bennett stewart born c  is an american lawyer journalist and author contents  early life and education  career  published works  awards  references  external links early life and educationedit stewart was born in quincy illinois he graduated from depauw university and harvard law school careeredit he is a member of the bar of new york the bloomberg professor of business and economic journalism at the columbia university graduate school of journalism editoratlarge of smartmoney magazine and author of tangled webs how false statements are undermining america from martha stewart to bernie madoff  he is a former associate at new york law firm cravath swaine  moore which he left in  to become executive editor of the american lawyer magazine he later joined the wall street journal where in  he won the pulitzer prize for explanatory journalism for his articles about the  dramatic upheaval in the stock market and insider trading these writings led to the publishing of his bestselling work of nonfiction called den of thieves  which recounted the criminal conduct of wall street arbitrager ivan boesky and junk bond king michael milken stewart became page one editor of the wall street journal in  and remained at the paper until  when he left to help found smartmoney stewarts book blind eye the terrifying story of a doctor who got away with murder  won the  edgar award in the best fact crime category disneywar  his book on michael eisners reign at disney won the gerald loeb award for best business book in  he was ranked st on out magazines  most powerful gay men and women in america he is currently a contributor to the new yorker and a columnist for the new york times which he joined in  stewart also serves on the board of advisory trustees of his alma mater depauw university and is past president of that board published worksedit stewart james  tangled webs how false statements are undermining america from martha stewart to bernie madoff new york penguin press isbn   stewart james  disneywar new york simon  schuster isbn   stewart james  flight in search of vision trenton africa world press isbn   stewart james  heart of a soldier a story of love heroism and september th new york simon  schuster isbn   a biography of rick rescorla morgan stanley security director who died at wtc stewart james  blind eye how the medical establishment let a doctor get away with murder new york city simon  schuster isbn   stewart james  follow the story how to write successful nonfiction new york simon  schuster isbn   stewart james  blood sport the president and his adversaries london touchstone isbn   stewart james  den of thieves new york simon  schuster isbn   stewart james  prosecutors new york simon  schuster isbn   stewart james  the partners inside americas most powerful law firms new york simon  schuster isbn   awardsedit stewart was inducted as a laureate of the lincoln academy of illinois and awarded the order of lincoln the state’s highest honor by the governor of illinois in  in the area of communications referencesedit  james b stewart indstateedu   stewart james b april   tangled webs how false statements are undermining america from martha stewart to bernie madoff   times hires james b stewart financial writer mediadecoder may     interview with stewart on den of thieves booknotes november     times hires james b stewart financial writer mediadecoder may     james b stewart gerald loeb award finalist ucla   oxfield jesse idov michael march   ‘out’ ranks the top  gays anderson is no  new york magazine archived from the original on june   retrieved june     times hires james b stewart financial writer mediadecoder may     board of trustees depauw university   laureates by year  the lincoln academy of illinois the lincoln academy of illinois retrieved   external linksedit official website common sense column archive at the wall street journal column archive at the new yorker appearances on cspan james b stewart on charlie rose works by or about ja